{"id": 1198, "genre": 1000, "title": "你对哪些被推崇的生活方式感到困扰？", "description": "一些生活方式被推崇之后，不遵从它们的人怎么就被放在了对立面？（题图来自：John F. Malta）", "record_count": 7686, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160901163807MbhyAu7mvnlx3jqk.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-17T17:00:20Z", "questions": [{"id": 1083, "title": "你对哪些被推崇的生活方式感到困扰？", "content": "你对哪些被推崇的生活方式感到困扰？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 112219, "content": "不爱“说走就走的旅行”，就被认为生活太死板", "image": "img/option/option/201609011642082sqt0YdXJSv7ZzWf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 112220, "content": "不喜欢听流行的音乐和影视剧，就被说“无趣”", "image": "img/option/option/20160901164320VpS4F9oj67BO2AWc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 112224, "content": "喜欢吃重口味的食物，被教育低油少盐的食物才是高级的", "image": "img/option/option/20160901165024swO2AGWHS67lPcUr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 112225, "content": "长胖了点就被质疑“管理不好自己身材的人也管理不好人生”", "image": "img/option/option/20160901165251Yz9P7GLCF8Hqbos1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 112227, "content": "对好吃的不感兴趣，被抨击不热爱生活", "image": "img/option/option/20160901165742kYbgKHUC5zQPA3hs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 112228, "content": "不爱运动也被爱运动的人鄙视", "image": "img/option/option/20160901170052Ig1zVme5dcXqHPtn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 112231, "content": "一夜之间大家都在说断舍离，我不愿意", "image": "img/option/option/20160901170324nIQSiNFbJf2sM3Ol.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 112233, "content": "不爱参加各种social活动，被扣上“难相处”的帽子", "image": "img/option/option/201609011706341HUZnCT2ekMgfmrL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}